          "summary": "Reviewed the dirty-tree daemon.rs slice (frozen snapshot snap-start/files/src/daemon.rs + dirty.diff, ~316 lines) implementing plan Task 3 (immutable session-home identity + additive/durable index_folder). The slice is TEST-ONLY: all 14 dirty.diff hunks for daemon.rs sit at lines >= 4841, inside `mod tests` (starts at 3995); the implementation in the frozen tree is byte-identical to HEAD, where `index_folder_for_session` still executes the destructive retarget (`std::mem::replace(&mut session.active_project_id, ...)`, HEAD:src/daemon.rs:1289, with old-project eviction at 1222-1249) and the tools.rs proxy failure arm still falls through to a destructive local reload (HEAD:src/protocol/tools.rs:6634-6800 after proxy_tool_call returns None). This exactly matches plan Task 3 Steps 1-2 (\"Replace retarget expectations with red immutable-home tests\", \"Prove the old destructive behavior\"): a coherent red-TDD checkpoint that compiles (all referenced symbols — with_project_root, new_for_test, new_daemon_proxy, bootstrap_project_index, IndexLoadSource::SnapshotRestore — exist at HEAD, consistent with the freeze-time cargo check pass) but whose ~7 rewritten/new tests would fail until Steps 3-5 land. The rewritten tests correctly encode design 4.2/5.1: home immutability on default and proxy paths, add=true as compatibility spelling with shared ledger replay, checkpoint receipt, snapshot durability with restore verification, and proxy-failure refusal. Two defects found in the tests themselves: the proxy-failure refusal test is non-hermetic and mutates the developer's REAL SYMFORGE_HOME daemon state, and the checkpoint contract's failure arm (degraded outcome, prior snapshot preserved) has no witness.",
          "verdict": "INCOMPLETE-SLICE — the dirty daemon.rs slice is a directionally-correct red-test checkpoint (plan Task 3 Steps 1-2) with the immutable-home/additive implementation still absent from the frozen tree; two test defects need fixing before the red suite is trustworthy.",
          "findings": [
            {
              "severity": "important",
              "scope": "dirty",
              "file": "src/daemon.rs",
              "line": 8322,
              "symbol": "test_index_folder_proxy_failure_refuses_destructive_local_fallback",
